                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/7603" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">CSR-0200</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1973 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">共享价值：绿城“幸福里”助力社区共治的社会责任进阶之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Shared Value: Greentown Promotes the Social Responsibility Advancement of Community Co-governance through &quot;Happiness Lane&quot;</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">曲亮，张智敏，肖迪，王伦，高玥</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">浙江工商大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">绿城服务集团</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">服务业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">13 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">共享价值；社会责任；绿城服务集团；“幸福里”；社区共治；2023百优案例</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Shared value; Social responsibility; Greentown Service Group; &quot;Happiness Lane&quot;; Community co-governance</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">党的二十大报告指出要健全共建共治共享的社会治理制度，社区主体之一的物业服务企业面临承担社会责任的机遇与挑战。本案例描述了绿城服务集团通过“幸福里”助力社区共治的社会责任履责历程：在原有“四保四乐”业务的基础上创新地提出“里长制”，以“业主带动业主”的方式拉近邻里关系。在党建引领之下，绿城服务搭建社区和业主的沟通桥梁，协调民生事务，承担部分社区治理职能。此外主动搭建共治线上平台，在企业联通下，“社区-业主-物业”三方进行党建共建，外部组织等也参与共创，实现共享价值的创造与外溢。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">The 20th National Congress of the Communist Party of China pointed out the need to improve the social governance system of co-construction, co-governance, and sharing. As one of the community entities, property service enterprises face opportunities and challenges in assuming social responsibilities. This case describes the social responsibility fulfillment process of Greentown Service Group Co. Ltd. in promoting community governance through the &quot;Happiness Lane&quot;. On the basis of its original &quot;Four Guarantees and Four Enjoyments&quot; business, the company innovatively propose the &quot;Lane Chief System&quot; to bring neighborhood relationships closer in a way that &quot;owners drive owners&quot;. Under the guidance of party building, the company builds a communication bridge between the community and the owners, coordinating livelihood affairs, and assuming certain community governance functions. Additionally, the company proactively builds an online platform for co-governance. Under the connectivity, the three parties of &quot;community-owners-property company&quot; collaborate together, and external organizations are also involved in joint efforts, achieving the creation and spillover of shared value.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《企业社会责任》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">第1题知识点为企业社会责任的内涵、类型、特征与演变；第2题知识点为共享价值式企业社会责任的履责动因与逻辑；第3题知识点为企业社会责任中利益相关者及利益相关关系；第4题知识点为商业模式视角下共享价值式企业社会责任的运作模式；第5题知识点为共享价值式社会责任的运作逻辑。</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023-10</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">查看全文:</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/7603" target="_blank">点击查看</a></td>
                            </tr>
